scrnval.condition:
type_code in ('FACILITY', 'FOSTERHOME', 'DAYCARE', 'FACDAYCARE', 'RESOURCE','SCHOOL', 'CONTRACT_FAC') 
and group_profile_id in (select group_profile_id from agency_group_link agl with (nolock) 
INNER JOIN agency_program_link apl with (nolock) ON apl.agency_program_link_id = agl.agency_program_link_id WHERE program_info_id =@param1 and agl.agency_id =@param2)
scrnval.description: type_code in ('FACILITY', 'FOSTERHOME', 'DAYCARE', 'FACDAYCARE') and group_profile_id in (select group_profile_id from agency_group_link agl INNER JOIN agency_program_link apl ON apl.agency_program_link_id = agl.agency_program_link_id WHERE program_info_id =@param1)

scrnval.condition:
group_profile_id =@param1
and (people_id =@param2 and status_approved = 1
or exists (select * from service_authorization_members sam with (nolock) where sam.service_authorization_header_id = tf.service_authorization_header_id and sam.people_id = @param2))
and event_definition_id =@param3
and program_info_id =@param4
and @param5 between date_from and dbo.GetDateEnd(date_to)
is_service_provider = 1 and agency_id =@param1 and staff_id in (select staff_id from staff_site_link with (nolock) where group_profile_id =@param2) and is_portal_user = 0
scrnval.description: is_service_provider = 1 and agency_id =@param1 and staff_id in (select staff_id from staff_site_link where group_profile_id =@param2)
